No. 11-7845. Eddie Hill, Petitioner v. James Cross, Jr., Warden. 565 U.S. 1174, 132 S. Ct. 1127,

181 L. Ed. 2d 1010,

2012 U.S. LEXIS 671. January 17, 2012.
